'''Glouroth''' was a [[dragon aging|mature adult]] [[Shadow dragon]] that resided in the [[Deep Wastes]] between the [[Lake of Shadows]] and [[Maerimydra]]. He made his lair in the [[Wailing Cliff]], an odd place where the [[Plane of Shadow]] bled into the [[Material Plane]].
